            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Samuel%2015%3A1-16%3A23%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_1%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Samuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESaul%20Defeats%20the%20Amalekites%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20Samuel%20said%20to%20Saul%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%20was%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20told%20me%20to%20anoint%20you%20as%20king%20of%20his%20people%2C%20Israel.%20Now%20listen%20to%20this%20message%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_2%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20has%20declared%3A%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20settle%20accounts%20with%20the%20nation%20of%20Amalek%20for%20opposing%20Israel%20when%20they%20came%20from%20Egypt.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_3%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20go%20and%20completely%20destroy%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E15%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20Hebrew%20term%20used%20here%20refers%20to%20the%20complete%20consecration%20of%20things%20or%20people%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20either%20by%20destroying%20them%20or%20by%20giving%20them%20as%20an%20offering%3B%20also%20in%2015%3A8%2C%209%2C%2015%2C%2018%2C%2020%2C%2021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20entire%20Amalekite%20nation%26%23x2014%3Bmen%2C%20women%2C%20children%2C%20babies%2C%20cattle%2C%20sheep%2C%20goats%2C%20camels%2C%20and%20donkeys.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_4%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Saul%20mobilized%20his%20army%20at%20Telaim.%20There%20were%20200%2C000%20soldiers%20from%20Israel%20and%2010%2C000%20men%20from%20Judah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_5%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Saul%20and%20his%20army%20went%20to%20a%20town%20of%20the%20Amalekites%20and%20lay%20in%20wait%20in%20the%20valley.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_6%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESaul%20sent%20this%20warning%20to%20the%20Kenites%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BMove%20away%20from%20where%20the%20Amalekites%20live%2C%20or%20you%20will%20die%20with%20them.%20For%20you%20showed%20kindness%20to%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20when%20they%20came%20up%20from%20Egypt.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20the%20Kenites%20packed%20up%20and%20left.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_7%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Saul%20slaughtered%20the%20Amalekites%20from%20Havilah%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Shur%2C%20east%20of%20Egypt.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_8%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20captured%20Agag%2C%20the%20Amalekite%20king%2C%20but%20completely%20destroyed%20everyone%20else.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_9%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESaul%20and%20his%20men%20spared%20Agag%26%23x2019%3Bs%20life%20and%20kept%20the%20best%20of%20the%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20the%20cattle%2C%20the%20fat%20calves%2C%20and%20the%20lambs%26%23x2014%3Beverything%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20that%20appealed%20to%20them.%20They%20destroyed%20only%20what%20was%20worthless%20or%20of%20poor%20quality.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_10%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Rejects%20Saul%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Samuel%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_11%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20sorry%20that%20I%20ever%20made%20Saul%20king%2C%20for%20he%20has%20not%20been%20loyal%20to%20me%20and%20has%20refused%20to%20obey%20my%20command.%26%23x201D%3B%20Samuel%20was%20so%20deeply%20moved%20when%20he%20heard%20this%20that%20he%20cried%20out%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20all%20night.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_12%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EEarly%20the%20next%20morning%20Samuel%20went%20to%20find%20Saul.%20Someone%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSaul%20went%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Carmel%20to%20set%20up%20a%20monument%20to%20himself%3B%20then%20he%20went%20on%20to%20Gilgal.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_13%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Samuel%20finally%20found%20him%2C%20Saul%20greeted%20him%20cheerfully.%20%26%23x201C%3BMay%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20bless%20you%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20said.%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20carried%20out%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20command!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_14%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20what%20is%20all%20the%20bleating%20of%20sheep%20and%20goats%20and%20the%20lowing%20of%20cattle%20I%20hear%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20Samuel%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_15%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIt%26%23x2019%3Bs%20true%20that%20the%20army%20spared%20the%20best%20of%20the%20sheep%2C%20goats%2C%20and%20cattle%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Saul%20admitted.%20%26%23x201C%3BBut%20they%20are%20going%20to%20sacrifice%20them%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God.%20We%20have%20destroyed%20everything%20else.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_16%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Samuel%20said%20to%20Saul%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BStop!%20Listen%20to%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20told%20me%20last%20night!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20did%20he%20tell%20you%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20Saul%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam1_15_17%22%20bk%3D%22sam1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20Samuel%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BAlthough